<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>통계 · k-ant-daily</title>
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ base_url }}/accuracy.html">
<style>
{% include '_theme.css.j2' %}
  body { margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--fg);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px; }
  main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 20px 64px; }
  h1 { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 6px; }
  header nav a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; }
  header time { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }
  section { margin-top: 28px; }
  section h2 { font-size: 16px; margin: 0 0 12px; }

  .empty { background: var(--card); border: 1px dashed var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
           padding: 24px; text-align: center; color: var(--muted); }

  .hero {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; gap: 20px;
    align-items: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--card), transparent);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 18px 20px;
  }
  .hero .big { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 900; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    color: var(--accent); line-height: 1; }
  .hero .label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .hero .meta { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
  .hero .meta strong { color: var(--fg); }

  /* Daily timeline chart (inline SVG) */
  .timeline {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
  }
  .timeline svg { width: 100%; height: 120px; display: block; }
  .timeline .grid-line { stroke: var(--border); stroke-width: 0.5; }
  .timeline .bar-hit     { fill: var(--pos); }
  .timeline .bar-partial { fill: var(--partial); }
  .timeline .bar-miss    { fill: var(--neg); }
  .timeline .bar-empty   { fill: var(--border); opacity: 0.4; }
  .timeline .y-label     { font-size: 9px; fill: var(--muted); }
  .timeline .x-label     { font-size: 9px; fill: var(--muted); }
  .timeline-legend {
    display: flex; gap: 12px; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .timeline-legend .dot { display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 2px; margin-right: 3px; vertical-align: middle; }

  .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr)); gap: 10px; }
  .card {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
  }
  .card .lbl { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }
  .card .val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; margin-top: 3px; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .card .sub { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }
  .card.high   .val { color: var(--accent); }
  .card.medium .val { color: var(--fg); }
  .card.low    .val { color: var(--muted); opacity: 0.7; }

  .day-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .day-list li {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto auto; gap: 10px;
    align-items: baseline; padding: 8px 12px;
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 13px;
  }
  .day-list .dt { font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .day-list .score { color: var(--muted); font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .day-list .score strong { color: var(--fg); }
  .day-list .rate {
    font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--neu-bg); color: var(--neu);
  }
  .day-list .rate.good { background: var(--pos-bg); color: var(--pos); }
  .day-list .rate.ok   { background: var(--partial-bg); color: var(--partial); }
  .day-list .rate.bad  { background: var(--neg-bg); color: var(--neg); }
  .day-list .retro-link {
    color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .day-list .retro-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .day-list .no-retro { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; font-style: italic; }

  .attrib-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .attrib-list li {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border);
  }
  .attrib-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .attrib-list .count { font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  .attrib-list .help { color: var(--accent); }
  .attrib-list .hurt { color: var(--neg); }

  footer { margin-top: 48px; padding-top: 14px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <header>
    <nav><a href="index.html">← 오늘자</a> · <a href="archive.html">📋 예측</a></nav>
    <h1>📊 통계</h1>
    <time>생성 {{ generated_at_display }} KST · 데이터 {{ totals.days }}일 누적</time>
  </header>

  {% if not records %}
  <section class="empty">
    아직 검증된 일자가 없습니다. 평일 저녁 20:10 NXT 마감 후 리뷰가 발행되면 여기에 쌓입니다.
  </section>
  {% else %}

  <section>
    <h2>전체 적중률</h2>
    <div class="hero">
      <div>
        <div class="label">누적 hit rate</div>
        <div class="big">{{ (totals.hit_rate * 100) | round(0) | int }}%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta">
        총 <strong>{{ totals.total }}</strong>건 예측 · ✅ <strong>{{ totals.hits }}</strong> ·
        🟡 <strong>{{ totals.partial }}</strong> · ❌ <strong>{{ totals.misses }}</strong><br>
        방향 정확도 <strong>{{ (totals.directional_accuracy * 100) | round(0) | int }}%</strong> ·
        검증 일수 <strong>{{ totals.days }}</strong>일
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>일별 추이</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      {{ timeline_svg | safe }}
      <div class="timeline-legend">
        <span><span class="dot" style="background:var(--pos)"></span>적중</span>
        <span><span class="dot" style="background:var(--partial)"></span>부분</span>
        <span><span class="dot" style="background:var(--neg)"></span>실패</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>신뢰도 버킷별 누적 적중률</h2>
    <div class="cards">
      {% for bucket in ['high', 'medium', 'low'] %}
      {% set s = by_confidence[bucket] %}
      <div class="card {{ bucket }}">
        <div class="lbl">신뢰 {% if bucket == 'high' %}높음{% elif bucket == 'low' %}낮음{% else %}중간{% endif %}</div>
        <div class="val">
          {% if s.total > 0 %}{{ (s.rate * 100) | round(0) | int }}%{% else %}—{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="sub">{{ s.hits }} / {{ s.total }}건</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>

  {% if attrib_sorted %}
  <section>
    <h2>신호 기여도 누적</h2>
    <ul class="attrib-list">
      {% for key, count in attrib_sorted %}
      <li>
        <span class="{% if 'help' in key %}help{% elif 'mis' in key or 'underestimated' in key %}hurt{% endif %}">
          {% if key == 'overnight_helped' %}🌙 간밤 신호 적중 지원
          {% elif key == 'news_misread' %}📰 뉴스 톤 오독
          {% elif key == 'overnight_misled' %}🌙 간밤 신호가 오도
          {% elif key == 'priced_in_underestimated' %}⚠️ 선반영 과소평가
          {% else %}{{ key }}{% endif %}
        </span>
        <span class="count">{{ count }}건</span>
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {% endif %}

  <footer>k-ant-daily · <a href="https://github.com/yummyummyummy/k-ant-daily" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></footer>
</main>
</body>
</html>
